#
# # Background 
# output eDP-1 mode 1920x1080 pos 0 0 bg ~/Pictures/Wallpapers/dharmx-Walls/mountain/a_castle_on_a_hill_with_fog_with_Eltz_Castle_in_the_background.jpg fill
